detaileddescription.para: Implementation of Spark's ColumnVector interface. The code for this class is heavily inspired from Spark's ArrowColumnVector The main difference is in how nullability checks are made in this class by relying on NullabilityHolder instead of the validity vector in the Arrow vector.
